      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just really stressed and honestly looking for any way to stay functional for these exams. if i can't do the st johns wort, is there anything else kind of natural or over the counter that i could take with my sertraline that actually is safe? something to just help me get through the next two weeks without having to deal with a whole doctor visit or prescription changes?",
